          <fieldset class="account-q">
            <legend>Do you Have an NREL/ESIF HPC Account?<span class="req">*</span></legend>
            <p>Select the option that is most correct for you:<span class="req">*</span></p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="isnreluser" id="isnreluser1" value="1" /> I already have (or have previously had) an ESIF HPC NREL account.</p>
            <p><input type="radio" name="isnreluser"  id="isnreluser0" value="0" /> I need a new ESIF HPC NREL account.</p>
          </fieldset>






          <fieldset id="existing-account">
            <legend>NREL/ESIF HPC Account Application Info</legend>
            <p>If you are an existing NREL user, or have previously had an NREL account, fill in the field below.</p>

